  "3292370": {
    "name": "SUBJECTS",
    "steam_appid": 3292370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c92fbe365aa7d30cf8c8abee5c35246d.avif?t=1759588099\" width=800 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SUBJECTS（受试者）</strong>是一款支持 4 人合作的生存恐怖游戏。你是“突袭者”之一，穿戴着Epoch Syndicate（新纪元集团）提供的装备，被派往搜寻他们声称早已废弃的研究设施。看似只是个简单的交易：为ES回收有价值的物资，领取报酬，为他们的“清理”行动出一份力。但在这层表象之下，隐藏着可怕的真相：这些突袭其实是另一种形式的实验。新纪元集团测试的是你的极限、你的意志、你的“人性”。而进入这里的人，从未真正离开过。逃脱只是幻觉；生存，才是你唯一绝望的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地底深处，被新纪元集团的操控所隔离与迷惑，你的意识开始崩解，现实与幻觉变得模糊。理智与被诱导的疯狂之间的界线，正在逐渐消失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/402637b2b3ac1bad5fdc2476cb9c2ba3.poster.avif?t=1759588099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/402637b2b3ac1bad5fdc2476cb9c2ba3.webm?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/402637b2b3ac1bad5fdc2476cb9c2ba3.mp4?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新纪元集团的阴影</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无处不在的新纪元集团，暗中操控世界，试图通过残酷手段强行进化人类。他们巧妙地利用像你这样的“突袭者”，以“清理任务”为名，深入废弃设施——实则是无情的人体实验。每一个突袭者，都是他们计划中的又一名受试者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c6ae551257eccb4ac285c3b25beb0581.poster.avif?t=1759588099\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c6ae551257eccb4ac285c3b25beb0581.webm?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c6ae551257eccb4ac285c3b25beb0581.mp4?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >永不停息的监牢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次“任务”都会将你的队伍投入一个全新的、程序生成的迷宫中。完成由ES指定的目标，搜刮战利品、升级装备——一切都在他们的监视之下。你将面对致命的敌人、断电、上锁的门和充满危险的环境谜题。这场“任务”，是他们对你耐力的严酷测试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/39cbc6b0cff1de92fe7bce265ff1fd33.poster.avif?t=1759588099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/39cbc6b0cff1de92fe7bce265ff1fd33.webm?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/39cbc6b0cff1de92fe7bce265ff1fd33.mp4?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你还能保持人性吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ES记录下你每一次挣扎，而你对现实的认知也在一步步被摧毁。无数突袭者在你之前已经崩溃、希望破灭。如今你也被打上了“受试者”的烙印，在他们可怕的设计中，是否还能抵抗控制，<strong>保有人类的本性？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c7c6b4958b1bfdaab1501647523542fe.poster.avif?t=1759588099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c7c6b4958b1bfdaab1501647523542fe.webm?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292370/extras/c7c6b4958b1bfdaab1501647523542fe.mp4?t=1759588099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>黑暗深入的背景设定与心理恐怖：</strong> 揭示ES的阴谋，守住你的理智。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的理智正在崩溃，你所谓的“逃脱”不过是个谎言。欢迎来到 SUBJECTS。你，就是实验本身。</p>",
